cess of $250 million dollars in numerous transactions in Europe and the U.K.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Mr. Harper received a B.S. in Management from Louisiana State University in New Orleans in 1969 and attended the Harvard Business School where he completed the Program for Management Development in the fall of 1988.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','William J. Harper','','publish','closed','closed','','william-j-harper','','','2021-03-04 22:49:02','2021-03-04 22:49:02','',0,'http://jeffcapstaging.wpengine.com/?post_type=team_members&#038;p=54',0,'team_members','',0),(55,2,'2021-02-25 20:33:32','2021-02-25 20:33:32','','Paul F. Giffin','','publish','closed','closed','','paul-f-giffin','','','2021-02-27 07:10:10','2021-02-27 07:10:10','',0,'http://jeffcapstaging.wpengine.com/?post_type=team_members&#038;p=55',0,'team_members','',0),(56,1,'2021-02-25 20:35:39','2021-02-25 20:35:39','','Francis T. Cazayoux','','publish','closed','closed','','francis-t-cazayoux','','','2021-03-04 22:54:42','2021-03-04 22:54:42','',0,'http://jeffcapstaging.wpengine.com/?post_type=team_members&#038;p=56',0,'team_members','',0),(57,1,'2021-02-25 21:04:12','2021-02-25 21:04:12','','Lester F. Alexander III','','publish','closed','closed','','lester-f-alexander-iii','','','2021-03-04 22:54:51','2021-03-04 22:54:51','',0,'http://jeffcapstaging.wpengine.com/?post_type=team_members&#038;p=57',0,'team_members','',0),(58,1,'2021-02-25 21:05:20','2021-02-25 21:05:20','','Joseph V. Truhe','','publish','closed','closed','','joseph-v-truhe','','','2021-03-04 22:55:00','2021-03-04 22:55:00','',0,'http://jeffcapstaging.wpengine.com/?post_type=team_members&#038;p=58',0,'team_members','',0),(59,1,'2021-03-04 22:56:46','2021-03-04 22:56:46','<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Thomas Davenport is an experienced financial services professional with over 18 years of advisory experience including, investment banking, corporate development, and restructuring. Mr. Davenport successfully executed over $15 billion in M&amp;A and financing assignments. He has experience with sourcing transactions, managing business development, leading industry verticals, hiring, training, and development of talent, and has served on deal approval committees. Mr. Davenport founded an investment banking platform and later merged it with a leading national accounting firm, where he served as Head of Special Situations and Private Capital Solutions and Head of the Industrials Coverage Team. He also has prior investment banking experience with William Blair &amp; Company and Citigroup Global Markets and Banking. Mr. Davenport has an MBA from the University of Chicago (2008), a Masters in Public Administration from CUNY-Baruch College (2006), and a B.A. in Business Administration from Morehouse College (2002).</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','Thomas Davenport','','publish','closed','closed','','thomas-davenport','','','2021-03-04 22:56:47','2021-03-04 22:56:47','',0,'http://jeffcapstaging.wpengine.com/?post_type=team_members&#038;p=59',0,'team_members','',0),(60,2,'2021-02-27 16:44:36','2021-02-27 16:44:36','<p>[vc_row][vc_column][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner][us_separator show_line=\"1\" thick=\"5\" color=\"secondary\" text=\"Our Founding Partners\"][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner][us_grid][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][/vc_row]</p>\n','Our Team','','inherit','closed','closed','','19-autosave-v1','','','2021-02-27 16:44:36','2021-02-27 16:44:36','',19,'http://jeffcapstaging.wpengine.com/19-autosave-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(61,2,'2021-02-27 06:45:43','0000-00-00 00:00:00','','Auto Draft','','auto-draft','closed','closed','','','','','2021-02-27 06:45:43','0000-00-00 00:00:00','',0,'http://jeffcapstaging.wpengine.com/?post_type=team_members&p=61',0,'team_members','',0),(62,2,'2021-02-27 06:49:23','2021-02-27 06:49:23','','Harper','','inherit','open','closed','','harper','','','2021-02-27 06:49:23','2021-02-27 06:49:23','',54,'http://jef